snippet.title: Lawman Guitars
snippet.description:
http://www.LawmanGuitars.com - Lawman Guitars is a Vintage Guitar & Rare Guitar Dealer located in Des Moines, Iowa. We specialize in buying, restoring and selling the best vintage guitars, rare guitars, used guitars and amplifiers.

Whether you're looking to buy a vintage guitar, find a classic guitar you remember from your childhood, or maybe you're interested in selling a guitar that's collecting dust in the attic, Lawman Guitars makes it easy.

We offer several classic guitars such as Fender Stratocaster, Gibson Les Paul, Danelectro, Rickenbacker, Martin and other acoustic guitars and used electric guitar and basses.

Contact Lawman Guitars and speak with Mike about finding the perfect guitar for you.
